sense.gloss: the Rabbit (fourth sign of the Chinese zodiac), the Hare
second month in the lunar calendar

meanings: sign of the hare or rabbit

sdata.j: ↑来年↑↓らいねん↓は|↑卯|↑↓うさぎ↓↑年↑↓どし↓です。
sdata.e: Next year is the year of the rabbit.
